  "description": "Map of the greater Strasbourg metropolitan area (France), from Strasbourg-Entzheim airport to the European institutions and across the Rhine to Kehl (Germany). 122k+ OSM buildings (binary format), 371k+ commuters with demand built from real INSEE census data, including a synthetic cross-border commuting model for Kehl. Strasbourg-Entzheim airport with runways and taxiways. The Rhine and Ill rivers fully modelled with depth data. Protomaps basemap with water, parks and forests.",
